  "content": "<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/image-15.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>又来这里看小动物了。其实我不是很喜欢小动物，因为味道。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"575\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/image-16.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>但是遇到了彩虹，所以有了这两张奇妙的照片。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"575\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/image-20.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>这是我更喜欢的场景，空无一人的农场。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/image-17.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>但是就是有很多羊。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/image-18.png?w=1024\" alt=\"\"></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>用屁股朝着我。</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"683\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://photoghenry.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/image-19.png?w=683\" alt=\"\"></figure>",
